export const weekDayNames=["Воскр.","Понед.","Вторн.","Среда.","Четве.","Пятни.","Суббо."];export const monthNames=["Янв","Фев","Мар","Апр","Май","Июн","Июл","Авг","Сен","Окт","Ноя","Дек"];export const getDate=function(e,t){const n=new Date(1e3*(e+t)),o=weekDayNames[n.getUTCDay()],s=monthNames[n.getUTCMonth()];return`${o} ${n.getUTCDate()}, ${s}`};export const getTime=function(e,t){const n=new Date(1e3*(e+t));return`${n.getUTCHours()}:${n.getUTCMinutes()}`};export const getHours=function(e,t){const n=new Date(1e3*(e+t)),o=n.getUTCHours();n.getUTCMinutes();return`${o}`};export const mps_to_kmh=e=>3600*e/1e3;